<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٧٩٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/676">إِسْمَاعِيلُ بْنُ أَبِي</a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٦١⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أُوَيْسٍ، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3976">ابْنِ وَهْبٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7248">يُونُسَ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5917">ابْنِ شِهَابٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4361">عُرْوَةَ بْنِ الزُّبَيْرِ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4781">وَعَمْرَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">عَائِشَةَ، </a>عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«تُقْطَعُ يَدُ السَّارِقِ فِي رُبُعِ دِينَارٍ.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>